The ATANT standard specification, story format specification, and testing methodology
documentation in this repository are made available for reading, reference, and evaluation
purposes only.

You may:
- Read and reference this work
- Evaluate your own systems against the ATANT methodology
- Cite this work in academic or commercial publications
- Share links to this repository

You may not:
- Redistribute modified versions of the standard specification
- Use the Kenotic Labs or ATANT name to imply endorsement of your product
- Claim ATANT compliance without publishing full results as specified in the standard

The narrative test corpus (story files), when published, will be made available under a
separate license permitting use for evaluation purposes.

